# Local environment — never commit real values; the pattern lives in .env.example
.devcontainer/.env

# Claude session notes — local observation list; promoted to CLAUDE.md or a
# skill only after user review, never committed
docs/notes.md

# Local issue/PR drafts — github-issue-creator, pr-draft, and their publish
# skills write here; drafts are ephemeral working files, never committed
.github/drafts/

# Subagent prompt captures from build-orchestration sessions — capture only,
# never committed; the README stays tracked to hold the rules
docs/prompt-log/*
!docs/prompt-log/README.md
